{"TopicId":223839,"ForumId":130,"TopicTitle":"V-SwiFT [v0.3.0]","CreatedByName":"cheese3660","CreatedById":226483,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-25T00:39:04Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"cheese3660","CreatedById":226483,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-25T00:39:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:24px;\u0022\u003EV-SwiFT\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nVariant Switching \u0026amp; Feature Tweaking, a part switch mod for KSP2\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nSpacedock:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://spacedock.info/mod/3562/V-SwiFT\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://spacedock.info/mod/3562/V-SwiFT\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nGithub:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/KSP2Community/V-SwiFT\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/KSP2Community/V-SwiFT\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nAuthor:\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/KSP2Community\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EKSP2 Community\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022PatchManager\u0022 data-ratio=\u002225.64\u0022 height=\u002220\u0022 width=\u002278\u0022 src=\u0022http://img.shields.io/github/license/KSP2Community/PatchManager\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:20px;\u0022\u003EDescription\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nV-SwiFT is a part switch mod for Kerbal Space Program 2, it allows modders to make variants for their parts such as changing out engine modes, increasing the mass, adding attach nodes, adding resource containers, removing resource containers, swapping out materials, etc...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:20px;\u0022\u003EImages\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cimg data-ratio=\u002246.87\u0022 width=\u00221199\u0022 alt=\u0022image.png?ex=65ea1117\u0026amp;is=65d79c17\u0026amp;hm=196c8dfa5ea4ad3f9e1caa1191e9ad19006e155acc80845a5be866ea359f4ca4\u0026amp;\u0022 src=\u0022https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1075863787862757437/1210302553896525884/image.png?ex=65ea1117\u0026amp;is=65d79c17\u0026amp;hm=196c8dfa5ea4ad3f9e1caa1191e9ad19006e155acc80845a5be866ea359f4ca4\u0026amp;\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\nAn example of the popout window for an engine mode switch variant\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:20px;\u0022\u003EHow to use?\u003C/span\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nThere is some documentation currently on the github wiki that is incomplete, the best place to ask for help is through me, or on the KSP2 Modding Society Discord\u003Cbr\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022text-align:center;\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:20px;\u0022\u003EDependencies\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cul\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://spacedock.info/mod/3277/Space%20Warp%20\u002B%20BepInEx\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003ESpaceWarp\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0(0.1.9.0 or later)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003Cli\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://spacedock.info/mod/3482/Patch%20Manager\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 style=\u0022background-color:transparent;\u0022\u003EPatch Manager\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0(0.11.0 or later)\n\u003C/li\u003E\n\u003C/ul\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KSRe-dev","CreatedById":232681,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-25T14:51:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks good, thanks for adding this\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d like to use something like this in KSRe instead of my inbuilt fuel switch, but currently it looks more complex and I can\u0027t see how to add a resource switch to test it, so I\u0027ll wait for those docs\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe best design I thought of was maybe 1 button in the part manager like you have, to toggle the fuel type, and then resource sliders below it, not sure if that\u0027s how it works but I\u0027m unsure if anything more complicated than that would be better than the current implementation I threw together\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyway good luck with the mod\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Safarte","CreatedById":227546,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-25T19:01:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224368615\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223839\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221708872700\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022232681\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KSRe-dev\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, KSRe-dev said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLooks good, thanks for adding this\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d like to use something like this in KSRe instead of my inbuilt fuel switch, but currently it looks more complex and I can\u0027t see how to add a resource switch to test it, so I\u0027ll wait for those docs\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe best design I thought of was maybe 1 button in the part manager like you have, to toggle the fuel type, and then resource sliders below it, not sure if that\u0027s how it works but I\u0027m unsure if anything more complicated than that would be better than the current implementation I threw together\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnyway good luck with the mod\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can find some examples of V-SwiFT patches with resource container switching here if you want: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/Safarte/KerbalLifeSupportSystem/blob/main/plugin_template/patches/part_variants.patch\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/Safarte/KerbalLifeSupportSystem/blob/main/plugin_template/patches/part_variants.patch\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KSRe-dev","CreatedById":232681,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-26T14:36:37Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224368666\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223839\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221708887717\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022227546\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Safarte\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 hours ago, Safarte said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can find some examples of V-SwiFT patches with resource container switching here if you want: \u003Ca href=\u0022https://github.com/Safarte/KerbalLifeSupportSystem/blob/main/plugin_template/patches/part_variants.patch\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://github.com/Safarte/KerbalLifeSupportSystem/blob/main/plugin_template/patches/part_variants.patch\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nis there a screenshot anywhere of how the resource switching works in game? in your mod\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Safarte","CreatedById":227546,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-02-26T19:56:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00224368818\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022223839\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221708958197\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022232681\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022KSRe-dev\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n5 hours ago, KSRe-dev said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nis there a screenshot anywhere of how the resource switching works in game? in your mod\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022o9KNwmP.gif\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002257.61\u0022 height=\u0022280\u0022 width=\u0022486\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/o9KNwmP.gif\u0022\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KSRe-dev","CreatedById":232681,"CreatedDateTime":"2024-03-04T21:17:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks, looks a bit complicated for this mod\u0027s situation of a single resource per tank\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}